`## LLM Quality Regression Runbook

### Step 1: Detect
Alert: llm_quality_score_rolling < 0.77 for > 2h
Signal: user regenerate rate up > 25% vs 7-day avg
Timeline: quality issues lag model changes by 2-4h (quality sampler runs async)

### Step 2: Isolate
